{"tid":1817694,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「又有巴打比狗咬」葵涌22歲男子被捕 涉元旦日向紀律部隊宿舍投雜物","createTime":"2020-01-09T09:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T10:00:41.000Z","uid":75778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bca2ab003c83a29567e51836a450e1ca02b5d2b4","tid":1817694,"uid":75778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T09:55:22.000Z","msg":"警方表示，一名男子於1月1日凌晨約3時，向葵涌葵蓉苑紀律部隊宿舍投擲玻璃樽及垃圾桶蓋。葵青警區人員深入調查後，昨日（7日）於葵涌區拘捕涉事22歲姓蕭男子，並於今日被控一項「醉酒及行為不檢」罪，案件將於下周三（15日）上午在西九龍裁判法院提堂。<br />\nsource by apple daily<br />\n<br />\n有冇人記得元旦日有位手足開post走咗入狗竇個垃圾房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d2687f285cb4110a529da6354461096283f2f66","tid":1817694,"uid":194298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T09:56:19.000Z","msg":"關佢事?"},{"pid":"4a9e7abdf42c5c9f0d88b2cc0ba47c357ed6915a","tid":1817694,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T09:56:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2265c95fab070f3ef955d7cc07742eeff9bbc68","tid":1817694,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T09:57:22.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 謝一謝位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaterials201920&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF0w1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=fe669534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/materials201920</a>"},{"pid":"49cbf40296bf7bc38556edabc68969e8128f349a","tid":1817694,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T10:00:21.000Z","msg":"換著其他屋苑發生 實hea查 乜嘢都查唔到"},{"pid":"8a84c74dde1d93f558c40e07130976bff65e219a","tid":181769